    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just a misconception though. i've lived it. some people are just born with a crack in them or something. no matter how much you try to patch it up, the cracks just keep coming back. it feels like a design flaw. i'm just tired of trying to fix something that was never meant to work in the first place.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
